author: JENELLE JANCI | Staff Writer
title: Friday YouTube Roundup: See what live music is in the area this weekend
text:
Shrimpboat will perform at Lancaster's Historic Elks Lodge on Friday, Oct. 16. 
Lancaster-area music lovers: your weekend guide has arrived. 
There are plenty of options if you’re looking to catch some tunes this weekend, from touring acts to local talent. 
Watch the accompanying YouTube videos to get a taste of each performer's style. 
Interested in learning more? Check out LNP’s features on Cindertalk and Beach Slang . 
FRIDAY, OCT. 16 
Shrimpboat, Jamall Anthony, Bjorn Jacobsen Where: Historic Elks Lodge, 219 N. Duke St., Lancaster When: 7 p.m., Oct. 16 Cost: $8
